channel.title: [showoff]test model[showoff]
channel.description:
Got bored and decided to stat making models again. Not like my old weapons models where I just copied the outline...Pasted...Then connected them, I actually worked hard on this'n. Lol. Anywho...Here it is:
EDIT: This is completely from scratch...Blah blah....Did not mean for the hilt to look like a sara star, that was an accident. Blah....This is just a test model anyways.
Rendering (Front View): [IMG]http://i553.photobucket.com/albums/jj374/AD_Setsuna/scimmy1.png[/img]
Side View: [IMG]http://i553.photobucket.com/albums/jj374/AD_Setsuna/scimmy2.png[/img]
Back View: [IMG]http://i553.photobucket.com/albums/jj374/AD_Setsuna/scimmy3.png[/img]
Other Side View (Points and Lines): [IMG]http://i553.photobucket.com/albums/jj374/AD_Setsuna/scimmy4.png[/img]
Doesn't have a name, so if anyone has any ideas....Please do throw 'em out there. :)
Constructive criticism is accepted and greatly appreciated!
